            <title>[BOOKKEEPER-187] Create well defined interface for LedgerCache</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/BOOKKEEPER-187</link>
                <project id="12311293" key="BOOKKEEPER">Bookkeeper</project>
